force - A USE flag that is unconditionally forced
mask - A USE flag that is unconditionally masked
normal - A normal USE flag that is never masked or forced
pkg-force - A USE flag that is unconditionally forced individually for a package
pkg-mask - A USE flag that is unconditionally masked individually for a package
pkg-stable-force - A USE flag that is forced on packages on a stable keyword only individually for a package
pkg-stable-mask - A USE flag that is masked on packages on a stable keyword only individually for a package
stable-force - A USE flag that is forced on packages on a stable keyword only
stable-mask - A USE flag that is masked on packages on a stable keyword only
